    "title": "Star Health Insurance is Hiring: Credit Analyst (Lead)",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Credit Analyst with drive and ambition, Star Health Insurance in Jaipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Star Health Insurance:\nStar Health Insurance is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Star Health Insurance!",
